Prosoma.
Carapace brown. Median band anteriorly heart-shaped, yellowish-brown, densely covered with white setae. Lateral bands brown (
Fig. 21
). Sub-marginal stripes yellowish-brown, wide and broken, marginal stripes black and narrow (
Fig. 21
). Sternum reddish-yellow, covered with short white setae and scattered long black setae (
Fig. 22
). Chelicerae reddish-brown, black posteriorly, densely covered with white setae and sparsely with black setae (
Fig. 23
). Clypeus yellow, covered with dense white setae and sparse black setae (
Fig. 23
). Labium reddishbrown anteriorly and black posteriorly, endites reddish-brown, covered with black setae (
Fig. 22
).
